About
=====
This script is colorized to Python's UnitTest Result.
inspired by RedGreen(rg command)

Install
=======
used to easy_install::

  $ easy_install pyrg


Require
=======
* Python2.6+


Usage
=====
basic usage::

  $ pyrg TEST_SCRIPT.py

  $ python TEST_SCRIPT.py |& pyrg


Configuration
=============
setting to $HOME/.pyrgrc file.
setting file example::

    [color]
    ok = green
    ng = red
    fail = yellow
    function = cyan

